Class AStar

java.lang.Object
StateSearch
UniformCostSearch
AStar
public class AStar extends UniformCostSearch
AStar or A* is a UniformCostSearch that calculates the smallest path between a layout start and a layout goal.

The differance between UniformCostSearch and A* is its Evaluation function, in A* we have a method that estimates the cost from a start to a goal, that evaluation function is then used in the priority queue so those who are closest to the goal are prioritised.

1.0 28/10/2023
